data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This charming 3BR, 1BA gem boasts a cozy wood-burning fireplace, ideal for chilly nights. Enjoy worry-free living with a new roof, hot water heater, and flooring. The expansive yard is perfect for families, pets, and gardening enthusiasts, offering space to expand and host outdoor gatherings. Convenience meets comfort with a prime location close to shops and main roads, making errands and commutes a breeze. Say goodbye to HOA dues, enjoy the freedom of property ownership. This home is eligible for USDA, FHA, and VA loans, providing accessible financing options. Imagine celebrating the holidays in this inviting space – move in and create lasting memories! This property is a fantastic opportunity for first-time buyers or those looking for a new space. Don't miss out. Schedule a showing today and explore the comfort and character that make this property truly special.
